  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK314">
<l>iṉṉācey tārai yoṟutta lavarnāṇa</l>
<l>naṉṉayañ ceytu viṭal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The (proper) punishment to those who have done evil (to you), is to put them to shame by showing them kindness, in return and to forget both the evil and the good done on both sides.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
